These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
Flower: sunflower, iris, bellflower, begonia
1. Flower:iris is on the left of Flower:sunflower##1
2. Food:mango == Flower:begonia##1
3. Flower:bellflower is on the right of Flower:sunflower##1
4. Food:pepper is on the left of Flower:begonia##1
5. Food:raspberry is on the left of Flower:sunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| Flower   | iris  | sunflower     | bellflower   | begonia |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Color: lilac, amber, yellow, emerald
Sport: parkour, soccer, swimming, volleyball
1. Color:emerald == Sport:soccer##1
2. Color:lilac is on the far right##1
3. Color:amber is on the right of Color:emerald##1
4. Color:emerald is on the right of Sport:swimming##1
5. Sport:soccer is on the left of Sport:parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Color   | yellow | emerald | amber | lilac    |
| Sport   | swimming    | soccer      | parkour | volleyball |

